div1.ab: Office of the Sheriff of King County W.T. | ss.
div1.p: I do hereby return to the Hon. Roger S. Greene, Judge of the District Court of the Third Judicial District that before the coming to aforementioned with the said Samuel Gowen and Donald Webster i am committed to my secretary, and are determined by write of another wit, ce copy of which is hereto connected; the orginial of which I also herewith produce; nevertheless I have the bodies of the said Samuel Gowen and Donald Webster before you on the day and place mentioned in said wit, as I am therein commanded.
div1.ab: Fees Service of Writ 2.00 Copy of Commitment 1.00 Travel of Miles .20 1 day attendance 3.00 Certificate .50 $6.70
